    "Clinical importance/relevance: Not important b.",
    "Rationale: Pantoprazole is the proton pump inhibitor of choice when coadministered with clopidogrel as it does not impact hepatic metabolism of clopidogrel to its active metabolite. 4.",
    "DDI: Methadone / Ondansetron a.",
    "Clinical importance/relevance: Not important b.",
    "Rationale: Low clinical concern for torsades de pointes when combining two medications with QT prolonging properties. 5."
